tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT  userId AS "users" , count(userSessionId) AS "log in/ nb connexions" FROM usersession WHERE ((useraction.application='SED - MyPLM QUL' OR userevent.application='SED - MyPLM QUL' OR usererror.application='SED - MyPLM QUL')) AND userId IS NOT NULL  group by userId ORDER BY userId ASC

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT Count(usersession.userSessionId) AS "nb users", usersession.userId AS "single user", useraction.name as "interaction users", useraction.javascriptErrorCount as "javascript error" FROM useraction where useraction.application IS "SED - MyPLM QUL" and useraction.javascriptErrorCount > 0 GROUP BY useraction.name,  useraction.javascriptErrorCount,usersession.userId ORDER BY count(usersession.userSessionId) DESC

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT userevent.page as "Page", COUNT(distinct userId) as "number visits", userevent.type AS "events" from usersession where useraction.application is "SED - MyPLM QUL" group by userevent.page, userevent.type
